title: Oreo Peeps Are The Latest Seasonal Flavor To Arrive On Store Shelves | Letty B | Y93
text:
Oreo Peeps Are The Latest Seasonal Flavor To Arrive On Store Shelves posted by Letty B - A post shared by Glenn Siepert (@gsiepert) on Feb 19, 2017 at 3:22pm PST 
Source: Instagram 
Okay, I must admit this sounds a little weird. But, I may give it a chance. Peeps Oreos were rumored MONTHS ago to come into existence for Spring/Easter - well they are here! 
The Peeps Oreos feature a golden Oreo cookie filled with artificially flavored bright pink marshmallow creme. 
The cookies are only available at select Walmart stores for the time being, but will roll out nationwide soon! Will you be trying this interesting mashup?
